r ChatGPT/Whisper ✅ Custom GPT development Expected Input: Audio/video course files, transcription requirements Expected Output: Whisper-integrated N8N workflows, accurate transcription system Rationale: Only expert with confirmed Whisper integration experience 📋 STEP-BY-STEP HIRING STRATEGY Phase 1: Initial Contact (Day 1) Contact Top 3 Experts simultaneously Send Project Brief: N8N Automation Expert Hiring SOP Request Quotes for 2-hour setup + ongoing support Phase 2: Technical Validation (Days 2-3) Screening Questions to Ask: Question\tExpected Answer\tEvaluation Criteria \"Describe your experience with N8N + OpenAI Whisper integration\"\tSpecific project examples\tMust mention actual Whisper API usage \"How would you handle processing 1000+ files without system crashes?\"\tBatch processing, error handling, queuing\tTechnical depth and reliability focus \"What's your preferred cloud deployment platform and why?\"\tRailway, Hetzner, or similar with reasoning\tCloud expertise and cost awareness \"How do you ensure 95% accuracy in automated transcription?\"\tQuality checks, validation steps, monitoring\tAttention to quality and processes Phase 3: Portfolio Verification (Day 4) Request 2-3 similar project examples Check references from bulk processing projects Verify N8N workflow samples Phase 4: Communication Test (Day 5) 15-minute Zoom call to assess: English communication skills Technical explanation ability Problem-solving approach Project timeline understanding 💰 COST ANALYSIS & NEGOTIATION STRATEGY Expert Tier\tSetup Cost\tHourly Rate\tTotal Project Cost\tValue Proposition Volodymyr K.\t$104 (2hrs)\t$52/hr\t$300-500\tPremium quality, proven results Eric O.\t$90-130 (2hrs)\t$45-65/hr\t$250-400\tSelf-hosted expertise Bhargav T.\t$70-100 (2hrs)\t$35-50/hr\t$200-350\tWhisper specialization Negotiation Tips: Offer milestone-based payments for security Request 3-month support package at discounted rate Ask for documentation as part of deliverables Include performance